      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a bit of a heavy distinction. If they both have no prior record and committed the exact same crime, why would the urban background in Case B be seen as an \"aggravating\" factor rather than just a circumstance? It feels like you're suggesting the environment itself makes the person more of a risk to society.",
